Martin Springer:

"this project is crucial for keeping the technology of digital media devices and services open to individual users. DirectFB is dedicated to creating a truly open standard for graphics, middleware and audiovisual applications for CE devices. The DirectFB 1.0 specification has been adopted by the Consumer Electronics Linux Forum (CELF) as an industry standard. Major CE manufacturers are CELF members."
(http://camorra.org/swann/?p=159)


